name: puttin' on the ritz...err...blockchain
description:
this is the seventh mint in a series: faces of the void

and also the fifth mint of a sub-series: the san fran chronicles

these are drawn using my fingers on an app on my phone

the drawings are simple and fun 

but the ideas behind are more complicated examining all the spaces in between the cosmic, emotional, spiritual, and interpersonal elements of the universe 

no, seriously
